    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Domestic structures with separate dwelling units for two individual families placed one above the other. When the units are placed side by side use "double houses."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
